*******************************************************************
To run the open-vm-tools at startup, add the following
settings to your /etc/rc.conf

vmware_guest_vmblock_enable=YES
vmware_guest_vmhgfs_enable=YES
vmware_guest_vmmemctl_enable=YES
vmware_guest_vmxnet_enable=YES
vmware_guest_vmsvc_enable=YES

For additional info about this setup, see
http://gromnitsky.blogspot.com/search/label/vmware
*******************************************************************
